# 09 - Diagrams

## Purpose

This document provides visual representations of the Nyx architecture.

The diagrams summarize concepts described throughout the documentation.

They are intended to improve understanding, not replace written documentation.

Whenever possible, diagrams should be authored using Mermaid.

